user_request: Search for Italian restaurants on Maps
screen_desc: This screenshot shows a Google search for "Italian restaurant." The highlighted restaurant, TGI Fridays, appears with images of its food and key details like the rating (3.9 stars from 1,394 reviews), its location, and operational hours. Options like "Dine-in," "Curbside pickup," and "No-contact" services are listed. There is also a link to view the restaurant's menu and a map to locate nearby TGI Fridays.
